Key.java for Adventure Time Created by: Jessenia Aguilar-Hernandez Modified By: Lauren Luo & Adrianna Valle This class creates Key Objects for the Game. It takes in the image name, the message that is given when the key is selected and a message that is given, when the key is not the correct one.
